data.value: select * from ( select T1.COLL_ID, T1.APPLIED_TO_CD, T1.COLL_DT, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CONCURRENT_IND, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.OTY_ID, T1.COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.PGM_APPLD_TO, T1.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO from CKT_COLLECTION T1 with(readuncommitted) where T1.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N' and ( T1.CREATED_TMST > @createdTmst1 and T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst2 and ( T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y' and T1.COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt or T1.ADJ_IND = 'N' ) or T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst1 and T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y' and (T1.COLL_ADJ_DT between cast(@date as date) and cast(@collAdjDt as date)) ) and T1.APPLIED_TO_CD = 'A' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'NAI' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'AFI' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'FCI' and T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst2 and T1.CRT_TYPE <> 2 and T1.CRT_TYPE <> 7 and T1.COLL_ID > @collId and exists ( select * from CKT_OB_TYPE T5 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T2 with(readuncommitted) on T2.CSP_SUP_NUMBER is not null and T5.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.OTY_TYPE and T5.DEBT_TYP_CD <> '718B' and (T5.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('A', 'M', 'N')) and T2.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' and T2.CPA_SUP_TYPE = 'S' where T2.OTY_TYPE = T1.OTY_ID and T2.OB_TRN_TYP = T1.OTR_TYPE and T2.OB_TRN_ID = T1.OTR_ID and T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T1.OBG_ID and ( T5.DEBT_TYP_CD <> 'MJ' or T5.DEBT_TYP_CD = 'MJ' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'AF' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'AFI' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'FC' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'FCI' ) ) ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) T1.NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON T1 with(readuncommitted) where exists ( select * from CKT_OB_TRN T3 with(readuncommitted) where T1.NUMB = T3.CSP_SUP_NUMBER and T3.OTY_TYPE = S1.OTY_ID and T3.OB_TRN_TYP = S1.OTR_TYPE and T3.OB_TRN_ID = S1.OTR_ID and T3.CPA_TYPE = S1.CPA_TYPE and T3.CSP_NUMBER = S1.CSP_NUMBER and T3.OBG_GENERATED_ID = S1.OBG_ID and T3.CPA_SUP_TYPE = 'S' and T3.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' ) ) S2 cross apply ( select top(1) NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON with(readuncommitted) where NUMB = S1.CSP_NUMBER and S1.CPA_TYPE = 'R' and S1.OTR_TYPE = 'DE' ) S3 order by S1.COLL_ID

data.name: ReadCollectionCsePersonCsePersonDisbursementTransaction
data.value: select distinct T1.COLL_ID, T1.APPLIED_TO_CD, T1.COLL_DT, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CONCURRENT_IND, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.OTY_ID, T1.COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.PGM_APPLD_TO, T1.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO, T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T4.CPA_TYPE, T4.CSP_NUMBER, T4.DISB_TRAN_ID, T4.TYPE, T4.AMOUNT from CKT_OB_TRN T7 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_COLLECTION T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN T4 with(readuncommitted) on T1.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N' and T1.APPLIED_TO_CD = 'A' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'NAI' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'AFI' and T1.PGM_APPLD_TO <> 'FCI' and T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst and T1.COLL_ID = T4.COL_ID and T1.OTY_ID = T4.OTY_ID and T1.OBG_ID = T4.OBG_ID and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER_DISB and T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE_DISB and T1.OTR_ID = T4.OTR_ID and T1.OTR_TYPE = T4.OTR_TYPE_DISB and T1.CRT_TYPE = T4.CRT_ID and T1.CST_ID = T4.CST_ID and T1.CRV_ID = T4.CRV_ID and T1.CRD_ID = T4.CRD_ID and T4.TYPE = 'C' and T1.CRT_TYPE <> 2 and T1.CRT_TYPE <> 7 on T7.OTY_TYPE = T1.OTY_ID and T7.OB_TRN_TYP = T1.OTR_TYPE and T7.OB_TRN_ID = T1.OTR_ID and T7.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and T7.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T7.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T1.OBG_ID and T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER is not null and T7.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' and T7.CPA_SUP_TYPE = 'S' and T7.CPA_TYPE = 'R' where exists ( select * from CKT_OB_TYPE T11 with(readuncommitted) where T11.DEBT_TYP_ID = T7.OTY_TYPE and T11.DEBT_TYP_CD <> '718B' and (T11.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('A', 'M', 'N')) ) and exists ( select * from CKT_DISB_TRAN T6 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T5 with(readuncommitted) on T6.DISB_TRAN_ID = T5.DTR_GENERATED_ID and T6.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE and T6.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER and @prqGeneratedId = T6.PRQ_GENERATED_ID where T4.DISB_TRAN_ID = T5.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID and T4.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_P_TYPE and T4.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_P_NUMBER )
